        <div class="price">$7,000–$13,000 unit</div>
        <p>Vulcan VR-36-1G24 (24-inch griddle right side), Garland M36-2G similar. Adds breakfast and short-order capacity.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="config-card">
        <h3>8-Burner with French Top</h3>
        <div class="price">$10,000–$18,000 unit</div>
        <p>Vulcan VR-48-FT, Wolf Challenger XL CHSC48-FT. French top is the solid plate cooking surface for simmering and specialty work.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="config-card">
        <h3>10-Burner Double Oven</h3>
        <div class="price">$14,000–$25,000+ unit</div>
        <p>Vulcan VR-60, Garland M60, Wolf CHSC60. Full-service kitchens running heavy dinner volume.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="config-card">
        <h3>Restaurant Range with Salamander</h3>
        <div class="price">$15,000–$30,000+ unit</div>
        <p>VR-60 plus integrated salamander broiler above. Salamander = high-heat finishing broiler. Pre-fire LA permitting required on new installs.</p>
      </div>
